name: wishlists
description: An e-commerce wishlist microservice developed using Agile Development PRactices with CI/CD pipeline and TDD and BDD testing. The application is deployed on IBM-cloud. Technologies utilized include Vagrant, Python Flask, Travis-ci,  Zenhub, Agile Development Process with CI/CD pipeline, with 98% Test coverage on all APIs. The database used is Postgres which is integrated using SQLAlchemy.
